<main id="main">
  <div class="inner-banner">
    <div class="bg-cover">
      <img src="/images/frontend/img05.jpg" alt="image description">
    </div>
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h1>Confidence Checkpoint</h1>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="confidence-rate-container text-center">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="approval-rate">Youâ€™re looking good!</span>
      <div class="bottom-text">
        <p>Congratulations! If the information entered so far is accurate, you have a strong chance of getting
          approved.</p>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-12">
            <a href="" id="termSheetBtn" class="btn btn-outline">Print Pre Approval Letter</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="/application/start" class="btn btn-default"> Keep Going - Continue Full Application <span
            class="hidden-xs">Online Now</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="why-box-holder">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-6">
            <div class="whyus-info-box">
              <h2>Why Choose Us</h2>
              <p>Commercial Direct provides alternative lending solutions that make sense for your unique business or investment needs.</p>
              <a href="/category/success-stories" nav-link class="btn btn-white">Check Our Success Stories</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-6">
            <div class="whyus-info-box about">
              <h2>About Us</h2>
              <p>Commercial Direct is an online lender offering loans from $250,000 to $2,000,000 on a wide range of commercial property types.</p>
              <a href="/about" nav-link class="btn btn-white">Learn More About Us</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="termSheetModal" class="term-sheet-modal">
    <div class="content">
      <div class="header">

        <span id="closeBtn" class="close">&times;</span>
        <a id="downloadTermBtn" class='btn' href="/download/loan-terms">Download</a>
      </div>
      <div class="body" id="pdfContent">
        <div>
          <img src="/images/frontend/cd-logo-color.svg"/>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 style="text-align: center;">Conditional Pre-Approval Letter</h2>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span> <%=: new Date() | formatFullDate %> </span>
        </div>
        <p style="margin-top: 15px;">
          This summary sheet is a basic outline of the terms and conditions currently being considered based on the
          initial information provided. This is not a commitment to lend, but merely an expression of our interest in
          providing the aforementioned financing request. The terms and conditions are subject to change in whole or in
          part at any time during the process including and up to the time that our due diligence, credit analysis and
          underwriting is complete.
        </p>
        <div style="margin-top: 10px;"><b>Borrower(s):</b> <%= req.user.name %></div>
        <div style="margin-top: 10px;"><b>Guarantor(s):</b></div>
        <div>
          <table>
            <tr>
              <td>
                COLLATERAL
              </td>
              <td>
                <%= (application.propertyAddress + ' ' + application.propertyCity + '. ' + application.propertyState) || '[]' %>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                LOAN AMOUNT
              </td>
              <td>
                $<%=: application.loanAmount | formatCurrency %>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                LOAN TO VALUE
              </td>
              <td>
                <%= Math.ceil(((application.loanAmount * 100) / application.propertyPrice) / 5) * 5 %>%
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                TERM
              </td>
              <td>
                <%= application.program || '' %> Years
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                AMORTIZATION
              </td>
              <td>
                <%= application.amortizations || '' %> Years
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                INTEREST RATE
              </td>
              <td>
                <%= application.resultingRate || '' %>%
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                INTEREST ONLY PERIOD
              </td>
              <td>
                <%= application.interestOnlyPeriodMonths || '0' %> Month(s)
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                ESTIMATED P&I PAYMENT PAYMENT
              </td>
              <td>
                $<%=: application.resultingMonthlyPayment | formatCurrency %>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                BUYDOWN POINTS
              </td>
              <td>
                <%= application.rateBuyDown || '' %> Point(s)
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                UNDERWRITING FEE
              </td>
              <td>
                $500.00 Up Front
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                PRE-PAYMENT
              </td>
              <td>
                Borrower will incur a 5% prepayment fee if the loan is repaid during the
                first <%= application.prepayPenalty %> years of the
                term of the loan
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                PURPOSE
              </td>
              <td>
                <%= application.loanType || '' %>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </div>

        <div>
          <p>
            Again, this is a Conditional Pre-Approval Letter and not a commitment to lend. These terms and conditions
            are subject to change. Please note that this outline does not contain all of the terms, conditions, fees and
            other provisions involved in this transaction that would be more fully described in the definitive legal
            document(s) for the proposed transaction.
          </p>
          <p>
            Should you wish to request Commercial Direct, a division of Silver Hill Funding, LLC to proceed with issuing
            a formal Letter of Intent under the general terms and conditions outlined herein in this non-binding term
            sheet, please submit the underwriting documents requested on the following page within seven (7) calendar
            days of the effective date of this letter.
          </p>
          <p>
            By submitting the documents below I/we desire to proceed with this transaction to obtain a Letter of Intent
            for pre-approved terms. I/we understand that I/we must provide additional documentation and information
            within the prescribed timelines.
          </p>
          <p style="margin-top: 10px;">
            <u>To begin the processing of your loan application, submit the following documents:</u>
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              Fully completed and signed application. Find our loan application here
            </li>
            <li style="margin-top: 5px;">
              If Purchase, fully executed Purchase and Sale Contract with all Amendments, Schedules, and
              Signatures.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 8px;">Sincerely,</div>
        <div><img src="/images/frontend/juan_barcelo_sign.png"/></div>
        <div style="margin-left: 8px; padding-bottom: 10px;">
          Commercial Direct, a division of Silver Hill Funding, LLC <br/>
          4425 Ponce De Leon Blvd. Suite 250 <br/>
          Coral Gables, FL 33146 <br/>
          Telephone: (305) 631-3784 <br/>
          Email: info@shf-commercialdirect.com <br/>
          Web: www.commercialdirect.com <br/>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  </div>
  <div id="editor" style="width:300px"></div>
</main>


<link href="https://calendly.com/assets/external/widget.css" rel="stylesheet">
<script src="https://calendly.com/assets/external/widget.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
<script>
  window.onload = function (e) {
    $(function () {

      $("#termSheetBtn").click(function (e) {
        e.preventDefault(); // if desired...
        $("#termSheetModal").css('display', 'block');
      });

      $("#closeBtn").click(function (e) {
        e.preventDefault(); // if desired...
        $("#termSheetModal").css('display', 'none');
      });

      $("#scheduleCallBtn").click(function (e) {
        e.preventDefault();
        Calendly.showPopupWidget('https://calendly.com/commercialdirect/15min')
      });

    });
  }
</script>

